Okukula amangu kw'obulwadde bw'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19) mu Bulaaya ne Bungereza wakati wa Jjanwali 1 ne Maaki 15, 2020.
Obulwadde bw'ekirwadde kya coronavirus (COVID-19) bufaanana mu mawanga ga Bulaaya/Ekitundu ky'Eby'enfuna ekya Bulaaya ne mu Bungereza, nga kino kiraga nti wadde nga waliwo enkulaakulana ez'enjawulo mu mawanga ag'enjawulo, COVID-19 eyongedde nnyo mu mawanga gonna.
Nga twetegereza ebyokulabirako bya Italy, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi birina okwongera okwetegekera obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obujja okwetaaga okujjanjabibwa n'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Nga 31 December, 2019, mu kibuga Wuhan ekya Hubei mu China, waliwo abantu abawerako abaakazuulibwa nga balwadde pulomoniya.
Nga 9 January, 2020, ekitongole kya China ekirwanyisa n'okutangira endwadde kyagamba nti ekirwadde kino kiva ku kirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuleetebwa SARS-CoV-2 bwatandika okuyitibwa obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19).
Okusinziira ku bubaka obuliwo leero, abantu nga 80 ku buli kikumi abalina COVID-19 balwala obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, obulwadde obw'omu mputtu z'omukka obulimu omusujja gw'amawuggwe oba obutaliimu, era abasinga bawona.
Kumpi ebitundu 14 ku 100 eby'abalwadde ba COVID-19 beeyongerako ne bawona ne beetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro, ate ebitundu 6 ku 100 ne beeyongerako ne bawona ne beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Omutwalo gw'abafa mu ddwaliro nga balina COVID-19 guli ku bitundu 4%.
Okunoonyereza kuno kuno kwekenneenya embeera y'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu European Union (EU) / European Economic Area (EEA) ne mu Bungereza era n'okugeraageranya n'embeera mu ssaza lya Hubei mu China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu UK n'ebyo ebya Italy okuva nga 31 January okutuuka nga 15 March 2020.
Embeera z'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
COVID-19 bwe yagwa mu China, yasaasaanira mu nsi endala era kati mu nsi yonna, COVID-19 ekyaguddewo mu China.
Nga 11 March 2020, akulira ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekiruma abantu.
Mu magazini ya Eurosurveillance eya Maaki 5, 2020, Spiteri ne banne baategeezezza ku bantu abaasooka okukakasibwa okuba n'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu Bulaaya, nga batuukiriza ebisaanyizo WHO by'esalirawo.
Abantu abasatu abaasooka okukakasibwa obulwadde mu EU/EEA baalagiddwa mu Bufalansa nga January 24, 2020  bonna abasatu baavudde mu kibuga Wuhan ekya Hubei mu China.
Okutuusa nga 15 March 2020, abantu abafunye COVID-19 bakiziddwa mu mawanga gonna 30 aga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, nga mu kiseera okuva nga 31 December 2019 okutuuka ku lunaku olwo, abantu 39,768 bebakwatiddwa n'abantu 1,727 abafudde, nga 17,750 ku bano, nga 1,441 bafudde, bali mu Italy yokka.
Okumanya omuwendo ogukendeera n'obulwadde obukendeera bwa COVID-19
Ekitongole kya Bulaaya eky'Okufuga n'Okuziyiza Endwadde (ECDC) buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'akawungeezi kikyusa ebitundu by'ensi yonna ebirimu abantu abalina COVID-19 okuva mu bitundu eby'obuyinza, gamba nga minisitule y'ebyobulamu, ebitongole by'ebyobulamu eby'eggwanga n'eby'ebitundu, n'ekitongole kya WHO.
Ebikwata ku kwongera kw'obulwadde buno bikozesebwa okunoonyereza ku ngeri COVID-19 gye yeeyongedde okusaasaana mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza n'okugeraageranya ne Italy.
Ng'ekiraga omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abazuuliddwa, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwazuuliddwa mu nnaku 14 bwakolebwa nga bwesigamiziddwa ku buzibu bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza okuva nga Jjanwali 1 okutuuka nga Maaki 15, 2020.
Era tuwaddewo omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa mu buli ggwanga ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'ekiro nga March 15, 2020, nga tugeraageranya ku muwendo gw'abalwadde mu Italy okuva nga January 31 okutuuka nga March 15, 2020.
Embeera y'okukulaakulana kwa COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Embeera y'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza yonna yali efaanana n'eyo eyalabikira mu ssaza lya China erya Hubei (ekifaananyi 1).
Obulwadde bw'ekika kya COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza okutwalira awamu bwatandika okulinnya nga February 21, era nga February 28, 2020 waayitawo okweyongerayongera okw'amaanyi.
Kino kyasinga kubaawo olw'okweyongera kw'abalwadde mu Italy, naye era mu nsi zonna ez'omu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, waliwo enkulaakulana y'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 (ebyongerezeddwako).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa nga balina COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza bw'ogugeraageranya ku muwendo gwa Italy ogwaliwo wakati wa 31 January ne 15 March 2020.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza kuno, omuwendo gw'abalwadde abaakazuulibwa ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'olweggulo nga March 15 mu mawanga amalala 15 aga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, gufaanagana n'ogwa Italy wiiki nga ssatu emabega.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti waliwo okweyongera okw'amangu mu muwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Embeera ezirabikira mu kulwala kwa COVID-19 ziraga nti kawumpuli eno ekulaakulana ku sipiidi y'emu mu mawanga gonna.
Kino wadde nga waliwo enjawulo mu nsi ez'enjawulo, enjawulo mu ngeri ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu gye bakolamu, era oboolyawo n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okumanya obulwadde n'amateeka ag'enjawulo ag'okulonda abalwadde okwekebejjebwa COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okugezesebwa.
Mu ntandikwa ya Maaki 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebyasannyalala baategeezezza nti abantu nga 10 ku buli 100 abalina COVID-19 beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, era bannamawulire baategeezezza nti amalwaliro n'ebitongole ebikola ku balwadde abali mu mbeera enzibu mu bitundu ebyo byali bijjudde.
Mu kiseera kino, obubaka obukwata ku kukkirizibwa kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu malwaliro ne (oba) ebitongole eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu EU/EEA busangibwa ku bitundu 6 ku buli 100 n'ebitundu 1 ku buli 100 eby'abalwadde (obubaka tebwaweebwa).
Kyokka, kyetaagisa okukuŋŋaanya obubaka buno obutegeke obulungi okusobola okujjuza ebikozesebwa mu kulaba omuwendo gw'abalwadde n'abafudde.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2010-2011 mu Bulaaya, waliwo enjawulo ey'amaanyi mu bungi bw'endwadde ez'amaanyi mu malwaliro ag'ekisawo n'amalwaliro ag'okulabirira abalwadde ab'amaanyi: okuva ku mirimu 29.2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku mirimu 4.2 ku bantu 100,000 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti amawanga amalala gayinza okuba nga galina obuyambi bungi oba butono okusinga Italy (ebisenge 12.5 mu malwaliro ag'ekisawo n'amalwaliro ag'okulabirira abalwadde ab'amaanyi buli 100,000 mu 2010/2011).
Lipoota ya ECDC ey'omukaaga ey'omulundi ogusooka ey'ebizibu bya COVID-19 eraga embeera ez'okukuba ebifaananyi ku by'obujjanjabi n'ebikebera ku by'okusiibula abantu abalina COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, ng'obutebenkevu bw'ebisenge mu malwaliro ag'ekisawo ekirimu obulwadde obw'amaanyi busukka ku 90%.
Olw'okuba mu kiseera kino obulwadde butegekeddwa mu bitundu bya EU/EEA ne UK, era amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi bitera okulabirira abantu ab'omu kitundu ekimu, amagezi gaweebwa okuwa obubaka ku bulwadde n'omuwendo gw'endwadde mu bifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi bwe kiba kisoboka, nga bwe kiba ku mutendera 2 ogw'ebitundu eby'obujjanjabi obw'enjawulo (NUTS-2).
Obuzibu bwa Italy n'ebikolwa mu nsi endala biraga nti COVID-19 ekulaakulanye mu EU/EEA ne UK.
N'olwekyo, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi birina okwetegekera embeera y'okussaako akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 ak'ekiseera ekiwanvu, n'okufuna obulwadde bwa COVID-19 obwetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kiri mu bitundu bya Italy ebyasannyalala.
Nga bwe kyalagiddwa mu alipoota ya ECDC ey'oluvannyuma ku biva mu kunoonyereza ku kabi, kikulu nnyo okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa SARS-COV-2 nga weeyongedde okukendeeza ku bulwadde, kubanga olw'okweyongera kw'obulwadde, abasawo n'amalwaliro bayinza obutaba na budde bumala kutegeera, kukola, n'okukyusa mu ngeri esaanira singa tebatandikiddewo.
Alipoota ekwata ku biva mu kunoonyereza ku kabi era eraga ebikolwa eby'ebyobulamu ebitegekeddwa okukendeeza ku bulwadde.
Amawanga galina akaseera katono okuzzaawo okufuba kwago okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'okuggyawo obuzibu ku nkola zaabwe ez'ebyobulamu.
Singa kino tekikolebwa, mu nnaku ez'omu maaso oba wiiki, enkola y'ebyobulamu mu nsi endala ez'omu EU/EEA ejja kufuna abalwadde bangi abajja okwetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Ekirwadde kya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), ekiva ku coronavirus ey'obulwadde obw'omukka obw'amaanyi (SARS) obw'ekika 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kyabadde kizibu eri abantu: mu kiseera kino abantu abasukka mu 3 000 bafudde mu China n'ensi endala era n'omuwendo gw'abalwadde gusukka mu 80,000.
Okufaananako akawuka ka SARS-CoV akaaliko akakwate akafaanana n'akawuka ako akaaleeta obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu mu bantu nkumi na nkumi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo eyinza okuyitibwa enkuyege era n'eyinza okuleeta obubonero obufaanagana nga ekozesa enkola y'emu.
Kyokka, COVID-19 si nzibu nnyo era tefa nnyo okusinga SARS, naye y'esinga okusaasaanya era ekosa abantu abakulu okusinga abato, n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Olw'okuba waliwo ebitabo bingi ebifulumidde ku bulwadde obwo, ekitundu kino kiraga ebintu bingi ebikwata ku bulwadde obwo.
Tujja kwetegereza ebintu ebikulu ebikwata ku bulwadde, ensibuko yabwo, obuwuka, okunoonyereza, okujjanjaba, okwetegereza n'okutangira obulwadde buno.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bingi bikyaliwo, tusuubira nti okunoonyereza kuno kujja kuyamba abantu okutegeera n'okumalawo obulwadde obwo obw'akabi.
Embaga y'omwaka omuggya (omwaka omuggya ogw'omu China), eya 2020 eyagwa nga January 25, yali ya njawulo era nga teyeerabirika eri abantu bonna ab'omu China, abaali bakubirizibwa okusigala awaka mu nnaku zonna ez'embaga n'olw'obulwadde bw'akawuka akava ku kirwadde kino.
Olw'okuba okufaanagana kwa maanyi ne coronavirus (CoV) eyaleeta obulwadde bwa SARS mu 2003, ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) ku 11 Febwali 2020 kyayita akawuka kano SARS-CoV-2, ate obulwadde obuli mu kiseera ekyo  coronavirus infection 19 (COVID-19).
Ekirwadde kino kyatandika mu kibuga Wuhan ekya China era ne kyanguya mu ggwanga lyonna era oluvannyuma ne kidduka ne kigenda mu nsi endala nga 50.
Nga 2 Maaki 2020, abantu abasukka mu 80,000 be bakakasibwa okuba nga balina COVID-19, abantu abasukka mu 40,000 be bawonye, era abantu abasukka mu 3,000 be baafa.
WHO yalabula nti COVID-19 ye "mulabe wa bantu omukulu" era asobola okuba ow'akabi okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu myezi egitawera ebiri, ebitabo ebisukka mu 200 byafulumizibwa ku COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'ebitundu ebikwata ku buwuka, obulwadde, enkola y'obuwuka, okunoonyereza n'obujjanjabi, okuva ku alipoota esooka eya Jjanwali 7, 2020, eyalaga obuwuka obwava mu balwadde abangi.
Okunoonyereza kuno kugezaako okuggumiza ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza mu kitundu kino ekiggya era ekikulaakulana amangu.
Bwe kiba kisoboka, tujja kugezaako okugeraageranya COVID-19 ne SARS n'obulwadde obulala obuva ku ssenyiga omukambwe (MERS) obwatandika mu 2012.
Era tujja kwogera ku ebyo ebimanyiddwa ku ngeri y'okwewalamu n'okulangirira obulwadde, awamu n'ebibuuzo ebirala ebikulu.
Koonavaayiruusi zaatwalibwanga ng'ezitali za bulabe eri abantu era nga ziviirako ebitundu 15 ku 100 eby'endwadde z'omukka 4.
Kyokka, emirundi ebiri mu kyasa kino, tulabye obulwadde bwa coronavirus obw'amaanyi obw'abantu, nga buno bwe bulwadde bwa coronavirus obw'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS-CoV-2) ne obulwadde bwa coronavirus obw'okuwummulamu obw'omu buvanjuba bwa masekkati (MERS-CoV), obwatandikawo obulwadde mu China mu 2003 ne mu Saudi Arabia mu 2012 era amangu ddala ne busaasaana mu mawanga amalala mangi nga bulwadde n'okufa bya maanyi nnyo.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 eyaliwo kati ye ssenyiga omukambwe ey'okusatu mu byafaayo by'omuntu.
Nga bwe kiragibwa mu kifaananyi 1.1, amawulire agakwata ku bifo omuli endwadde z'amawuggwe ag'ekika ekitamanyiddwa gaasooka okuweebwa ekitongole kya China eky'ebyobulamu okuva mu kibuga Wuhan nga Ddesemba 31, 2019.
Nga wayise ennaku musanvu, omutendera gwa bakensa ba virus gwafulumizibwa.
Nga 15 January, 2020, omuntu eyasooka okufa yazuulibwa mu kibuga Wuhan.
Mu kiseera kye kimu, obulwadde buno bwasaasaana mangu mu bibuga, mu bitundu, ne mu nsi eziriraanyewo.
Nga January 20, kyamanyiddwa nti abasawo bafunye obulwadde buno, ekyaleetera abantu okulowooza nti obulwadde buno busobola okusasaana okuva ku muntu okudda ku mulala.
Nga January 23, mu kibuga Wuhan, ekirwadde kya bannakampala kyayisibwa, era ne ttivvi y'ebidduka by'omu kibuga yalekera awo okukola.
Nga January 24, okunoonyereza okwasooka okwaliwo kwalaga nti abalwadde 21 ku 41 abaakakasibwa obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe baakolagana butereevu n'akatale k'eby'ennyanja mu kibuga Wuhan, ekyatwalibwa okuba ekifo ekikulu ekyandiyisizza obulwadde buno okuva mu nsolo etamanyi.
Nga January 30, WHO yalangirira nti ekirwadde kya coronavirus kye kyabaddewo mu nsi yonna nga kijjanjaba abantu.
