Ekisooka mu kulwanyisa akabi k'obulwadde buno kwe kwambala masiki; era n'amasiki ag'okujjanjaba n'ebyuma ebikuuma omukka ebiri mu nnamba N95 (series No. 1860s) biyamba okuziyiza obulwadde.
Bbalaza ez'okujanjaba ziziyiza amatanzi g'amazzi okuva mu bantu abalina obulwadde okubuuka mu bbanga ne gabeera ku bintu ebiyinza okuleeta obulwadde.
Kyokka, masiki za N95 zokka (series No. 1860s) ze zisobola okukuuma okuva ku vironi eziri wakati wa 10 ne 80 nm, era ziwa 5% zokka eziri wakati wa 5 ne 80 nm; akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 kalina obunene nga SARS-CoV, era zombi ziri 85 nm.
Olw'okuba obutundutundu busobola okuyita ne mu masiki etaano ez'okujjanjaba nga zigattiddwa wamu, abasawo abakwatagana n'abalwadde balina okwambala masiki ez'ekika kya N95 (serial No. 1860s) so si masiki ez'okujjanjaba.
Ng'oggyeko obusozi, abakozi b'obujjanjabi basaanidde okwambala engoye ez'okukuuma omubiri okusobola okukendeeza ku mikisa egiri mu kwetaba n'akawuka.
Obuwuka era buyinza okuyingira mu mubiri okuyita mu maaso.
Nga 22 January, 2020, omusawo yafuna SARS-CoV-2 wadde nga yali ayambadde ekikookolo kya N95; oboolyawo akawuka kaayingira mu mubiri gwe okuyita mu maaso agaali gaakaaba.
N'olwekyo, abasawo basaanidde okwambala ebikozesebwa mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Abantu bonna abali mu bitundu ebikoseddwa oba ebiyinza okubaako akabi bakubirizibwa okunaaba engalo zaabwe n'amazzi ag'okusaasaanya akawuka, okwewala okufuluma awaka, okweyawula ku bantu abalala, n'okukendeeza ku nkolagana n'abantu abalina akawuka.
Ekitundu ekituufu eky'okubeera n'omulwadde kiri mu ffuuti nga ttaano.
Ebintu bino biyamba okukendeeza ku buzibu bw'okulwala n'okutangira akawuka okusaasaana.
Wadde nga akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 kaali tekamanyiddwa, okufaananako kwaakwo ne SARS-CoV okwategeezebwa nga January 7, 2020, kwali kulina okuba akabonero ak'okweraliikiriza eri China, ng'olowooza ku ebyo bye yali ayiseemu mu kiseera kya SARS mu 2003.
Kyokka, nga January 19, 2020, akulira ekitongole kya Wuhan Disease Control Center yakkakkanya abantu ng'agamba nti akawuka akapya tekalina buwuka bungi era tekasobola kusasaana okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu era nti okuziyiza n'okufuga obulwadde tebirina kuba buzibu.
Ekiragiro kino kyawukanye nnyo obutategeeragana mu bantu naddala mu kiseera ng'eggwanga lyonna lyeteekateeka ku mukolo gw'okukuza omwaka omuggya era nga kyabulako akaseera ak'amaanyi ekirwadde kino we kyandikulidde mu kibuga Wuhan nga tewali muntu yenna afiiridde.
Abakulira eby'obulamu mu China basobola okuyiga ku kizibu kino era ne bakola enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu balina: (1) okwekuuma nga boogera eri abantu kubanga buli kigambo abantu kye boogera kisobola okukwata ku ndowooza yaabwe n'ebyo bye basalawo; (2) okwekuuma n'okuddamu mu bubaka obutali bwa bulijjo obuva mu malwaliro mu kifo ky'okulindirira alipoota okuva eri abasawo n'abakungu; (3) okuba abamalirivu okuziyiza ekirwadde mu biseera eby'omu maaso mu kifo ky'okukuuma abantu nga si bakkakkamu; ne (4) okwenyigira mu kutendekebwa okw'amaanyi okw'okuyamba abantu okumanya obulwadde n'okukebera n'okulongoosa enkola y'okuddamu.
Obulwadde bwa COVID-19, obwaleetebwawo ssenyiga omukambwe ow'ekika eky'okubiri (SARS-CoV-2), bwatandika mu nkomerero ya December 2019.
Mu myezi ebiri gyokka, obulwadde buno bwali bubuutikidde China yonna era nga bwe nnali mpandiika, bwali busangiddwa mu nsi 50.
Olw'okuba akawuka kalifaanana nnyo ne coronavirus ey'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS-CoV) era n'obubonero bwa COVID-19 nga bwe bumu n'obubonero bw'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS), obulwadde bwa COVID-19 buyinza okuleetera omuntu okuwulira ng'awera SARS.
Kyokka waliwo enjawulo enkulu wakati wa COVID-19 ne SARS, nga nkulu nnyo mu kuziyiza ekirwadde n'okujjanjaba abalwadde.
COVID-19 ekosa abantu abakulu okusinga abavubuka, n'abasajja okusinga abakazi; n'omuwendo gw'abalwadde abakulu n'okufa nabyo bisingawo ku by'abavubuka.
Okufa okuva mu SARS kusingawo ku kwa COVID-19 (10,91 % bw'ogigeraageranya ne 1,44 %).
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 basaasaanya akawuka ne bwe baba nga tebalina bubonero, ate abalwadde ba SARS batera okusasaanya abalala mu mbeera ez'amaanyi, n'olwekyo okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa COVID-19 kizibu okusinga SARS.
Kino ky'ekimu ku by'ensonga lwaki SARS-CoV-2 esaasaana mangu era mu bungi okusinga SARS-CoV.
Abalwadde abamu abalina COVID-19 bayinza okuba nga balina ebipimo ebya bulijjo eby'omusaayi ogutaali gwa SARS-CoV-2 RNA.
Ku luuyi olulala, abalwadde abawonyezebwa bayinza okuddamu okukeberebwa ne balaga nti balina akawuka.
Bino byonna byongera nnyo akabi ak'ekirwadde kino okusaasaana.
Mu kunoonyereza okw'amangu ku COVID-19, waliwo ebibuuzo ebikulu ebikyaliwo:
SARS-CoV-2 yava wa?
Wadde nga waliwo okufaanagana kwa bitundu 96 ku buli kikumi wakati wa SARS-CoV-2 ne ssenyigaalo Coronaviruses bbiri eziringa SARS, tetukyasobola kugamba nti obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwava mu ssenyigaalo.
Ensolo ki eyafuuka ekika ekirala ekyasobozesa akawuka okuva ku muntu eyasooka, gamba ng'empologoma, n'atuuka ku muntu?
Bwe tutamanya bya kuddamu mu bibuuzo bino, tetusobola kukendeeza ku ngeri y'okusomesezaamu obulwadde buno, era embeera y'obutafa eyinza okwongera okwonooneka ekiseera kyonna.
Okuteeka mu nkola ebyuma n'ebimera byalaga nti SARS-CoV-2 ekwatagana ne ACE2, naye omukka guyingira gutya mu butoffaali bw'omukka ne guleeta enkyukakyuka?
Omusaayi gukwatagana n'obutoffaali obufulumya ACE2 mu bitundu ebirala?
Bwe tutaba na by'okuddamu ebituufu ku bibuuzo ebyo, tetusobola kulaba bulwadde buno mu bwangu era ne tubulwanyisa mu ngeri ey'omuganyulo.
Obulwadde buno bunaabaawo kumala bbanga ki?
Omusaayi guva ku muntu okudda ku mulala gutya?
Kyandiba nti kijja kuleetawo kawumpuli w'ensi yonna, oba nti kijja kuggwaawo nga SARS, oba nti kijja kuddamu okujja ng'omusujja?
Ebintu bino bikulu nnyo, naye kijja kutwala ekiseera okufuna eby'okuddamu mu bibuuzo bino n'ebirala bingi.
Kyokka, tetulina kya kukola okuggyako okuziyiza kawumpuli ono amangu ddala nga bwe kisoboka era n'okudda mu bulamu obwa bulijjo.
Ensibuko y'obulwadde bwa coronavirus okuva mu nsolo
Okukyuka n'okukyusa ebitundu by'omubiri biviiriddeko obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (CoV) n'abantu okufuuka ebiramu okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka.
Okutuusa mu 2003, abantu baali bamanyi nti waliwo obulwadde bwa korona obwa buli ngeri obubiri obuyitibwa human coronavirus (HCoV) obuleeta obulwadde obutonotono, gamba ng'omukka.
Obulwadde bwa SSARS ne MERS bukyusizza endowooza yaffe ku ngeri omuntu gy'ayinza okuyitamu obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe.
Okujja kwa ssenyiga omukambwe ow'obulwadde bw'omukka obw'ekika eky'okubiri (SARS-CoV-2) mu China wakati mu 2019 kyaddamu okuleeta essira ku ssenyiga omukambwe era ne kitwewuunyisa olw'obutafaanana bwa ssenyiga omukambwe mu ngeri ey'enjawulo okusinga ssenyiga omukambwe SARS-CoV.
Obuwuka bwa coronavirus mu bantu bulwadde bwa nsolo, era okutegeera ensibuko yabwo kijja kuba kya muganyulo nnyo.
Koonavaayirasi z'abantu ezisinga ziva mu nkumba, nga tezirina bulwadde.
Era waliwo n'ebisenge ebirimu obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe.
Okutondawo ebisolo ebisaasaanya endwadde kiyamba nnyo mu kuziyiza endwadde z'abantu okusaasaana.
Okunoonyereza ku ngeri ebisolo gye bikwataganamu ne coronavirus era kiyinza okuyamba mu kumanya ekiddukano kya coronavirus mu bantu.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, tulabye ebikwatako koronavairusi musanvu ez'abantu, nga tussa essira ku byafaayo by'okunoonyereza, n'engeri gye zaatandikamu n'engeri gye zaayitiramu.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti tugeraageranya ne tulwanyisa koronaavairusi ez'enjawulo ez'abantu mu ngeri y'okukulaakulana kwa virus n'okuzzaawo genome.
Mu mbeera eno, ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekyazuulibwa mu 2019 (COVID-19) nakyo kyogerwako.
Ate era, ebisaanyizo ebyetaagisa okusobola okukyusa abajjanjabi n'obutonde, n'engeri enkulaakulana y'akawuka gye ekwata ku bulwadde.
Coronaviruses ziri mu maka ga Coronaviridae, nga zino ze zimu ku z'obutwa ezirina omutindo gumu ogwa RNA.
Enkoko zino ezirina genome esinga obunene mu z'omulwadde ezirimu RNA, nga zirimu obuwumbi 26 okutuuka ku 32, ziyitibwa bwe zityo olw'engeri gye zifaananamu ng'engule bw'ozitunuulira wansi wa microscope.
Okusinziira ku nkola, koronavirusi zirina genome ezitali za kuwulibwamu era nga zirina enkola y'emu.
Kumpi ebitundu bibiri bya kusatu eby'omutindo gwa genome birimu ebitundu bibiri ebinene eby'okubala (ORF1a ne ORF1b) ebikubisaamu ebitundu ebyenjawulo, ebikubisaamu ebitundu ebyenjawulo eby'omutindo gwa pp1a ne pp1ab.
Amagi gano gayitibwa nsp1~16 era nga gafuulibwa amagi amalala 16.
Ekitundu ekisigaddewo eky'omulongooti kirimu ebitundu ebikalu by'amagi agali mu ngeri ey'enjawulo, omuli amagi agali mu mpeke (S), amagi agali mu lususu (E), amagi agali mu lususu (M), ne amagi agali mu nnamutabu (N).
Mu ngeri y'emu, mu ngeri endala, waliwo obutoffaali obumu obuyitibwa line-specific accessory protein.
Okusinziira ku njawulo mu mpisa z'amagi\ coronaviruses, zaawukana mu bika bina (alpha, beta, gamma- ne delta coronaviruses), ate beta coronaviruses eziri mu bika bino zirimu koronavirusi z'abantu ezisinga obungi era zaawukana mu mitendera ena (A, B, C ne D).
Waliwo obujulizi bwa phylogenetic obulaga nti ensolo ez'ekika kyazo ezisinga ze alfa- ne beta coronaviruses, enyonyi ze zisinga okuteekawo gamma ne delta coronaviruses.
Okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka, obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe buva ku bika by'abantu ne buva ku bika by'abantu, era abamu ku bo bafuuka endwadde ez'akabi eri abantu.
Okutuusa kati waliwo abantu musanvu abalina akawuka ka corona.
Mu bano mwe muli alpha-coronavirus z'abantu HCoV-229E ne HCoV-NL63.
Beta coronaviruses endala etaano zirimu HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus ey'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (SARS-CoV), coronavirus ey'obulwadde bw'okuwummulamu obw'omu Buvanjuba (MERS-CoV) ne coronavirus ey'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu obw'ekika eky'okubiri SARS-CoV-2.
Kookoloowaayiriisi z'abantu HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 ne HCoV-NL63 zitera okuleeta obubonero obutonotono, gamba ng'omukka n'okusannyalala.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, akawuka ka SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, ne SARS-CoV-2 akazuulibwa gye buvuddeko awo, kalwadde nnyo, era kaviirako endwadde ez'amaanyi ez'omu mputtu ez'okuwummulamu mu balwadde abangi nga balina obwetaavu bw'okufuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (ALS) n'obubonero obw'enjawulo.
Ekikopo ekisooka ekya HCoV-229E, B814, kyaggibwa mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abaalina obulwadde bw'ensusu mu myaka gya 1960.
Okuva olwo, okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi kuleese okumanya okw'enkukunala ku kawuka ka HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43, akooleka obubonero bw'obulwadde obw'omu kitundu.
Mazima ddala, ng'obulwadde bwa SARS tebunnabalukawo, abantu bangi baali balowooza nti omuntu okufuna akawuka ka coronavirus tekirina kabi konna.
Ekirwadde kya SARS mu 2003 kye kimu ku bikyasinze okutabangula abantu mu byafaayo; abantu abasukka mu 8,000 baalwala era omuwendo gw'abafa gwali kumpi 10%.
Nga wayise emyaka kkumi, obulwadde bwa Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) bwabalukawo mu kitundu kya Buwalabu ne bucaase nnyo, era obulwadde obwo ne busasaana mu nsi endala.
Kolonavaayirasi empya eya muntu (2019-nCoV) eyazuulibwa mu 2019, oluvannyuma eyatuumibwa SARS-CoV-2, ye yaleeta obulwadde bw'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe ekya 2019 (COVID-19), ekitta abantu abasukka mu 3,120 nga 3 March 2020 era n'abantu abasukka mu 91,000 abafunye obulwadde buno.
Omusango gw'obulabe gukutte era ensi erina okwetegekera ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 ekinaatera okubaawo.
Obuwuka bwonna omusanvu obuyitibwa human coronaviruses buva mu nsolo, era buva mu nsolo, emmese oba ebisolo.
Ebikwata ku bukakafu bungi biraga nti abantu bonna abalina akawuka ka corona bavudde mu mbuzi, nga zino ze zaaliko obuwuka obwamanyiddwa obulungi era nga tezirina bulwadde bwonna naye nga zirina obwenjawulo bungi.
Ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kivuddeko China n'ensi yonna okugezesebwa okw'amaanyi mu by'ekisawo, mu bya sayansi, mu by'obulamu n'empisa.
Okunoonyereza ku ngeri ssemaka gye yajjawo, kijja kuyamba okutegeera ebyafaayo by'obulwadde bwa ssemaka, ebireetera abantu okukulaakulana, n'ebintu ebiyinza okulemesa abantu okubufuna.
Kiyinza n'okulaga oba okwanguya okunoonya ekikonde, ekirwadde ekirimu SARS-CoV-2 ekirimu ekirwadde ekirimu ekirwadde ekirala, ekikulu nnyo mu kuziyiza obulwadde okucaaka mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Okunoonyereza kuno kuzingiramu okumanya ku nsibuko y'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe, okuyitibwa kw'obulwadde bw'abantu n'engeri gye buvaamu.
Naddala, tutegeeza era ne twekenneenya ekintu kino ekikulu: akawuka akasooka akaviirako abantu okulwala ssenyiga omukambwe, tekateekamu bulwadde, naye bwe kafuluma mu bika ne kakwata ku muntu omulala.
Era twekenneenya enkulaakulana y'obulwadde bwa coronavirus mu bantu, nga bweyoleka nti okuzuukuka kw'obulwadde buno emirundi mingi kubaako obuzibu.
Mu mbeera y'emu, ebiva mu kawumpuli wa SARS-CoV-2 kati nabyo bitwalibwa.
Koonavaayiruusi z'ebisolo zimanyiddwa okuva ku nkomerero y'emyaka gya 1930.
B814 eya HCoV-229E nga tennaba kuzuulibwa mu bantu abaalina obulwadde bw'ensusu, koronavairusi ez'enjawulo zaali mu nsolo ez'enjawulo, omwali enkoko, embuzi, ente, embizzi, embwa n'embwa.
Mu myaka egyakayita, waliwo abantu musanvu abazuuliddwa nga balina ssenyiga omukambwe.
Mu kipande 1 waliwo ebyafaayo ebitonotono eby'abantu abafunye akawuka ka ssenyiga omukambwe mu ngeri ey'obudde.
Ekika ekisooka ekya HCoV-229E kyazuulibwa okuva mu bibala eby'omu mputtu z'omukka mu balwadde abaalina endwadde ez'omu mputtu ez'omu mputtu ez'omu waggulu mu 1966; oluvannyuma akawuka kano kaali kakkiriziganyizza n'okweyongera mu mibiri gy'obutoffaali bw'omutima WI-38.
Abalwadde abalina akawuka ka HCoV-229E baayolesezza obubonero bw'enkuba, omuli omutwe, okusensera, obulumi mu bulago, n'omusujja mu bulago, ate nga omusujja n'okusensera byaliwo mu bitundu 1020 ku buli kikumi.
Oluvannyuma, mu 1967, akawuka ka HCoV-OC43 kaawangulwa okuva mu bitundu by'omubiri n'okufuluma mu bwongo bw'empiso.
Obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa HCoV-OC43 bufaanana n'obw'obulwadde bwa HCoV-229E, obufaanana obuwuka obuyitibwa influenza A ne rhinovirus.
Ensi yonna erimu akawuka ka HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43 era nga kafuluma mu biseera by'obutiti.
Mu ngeri enkulu, akawuka kano kabeerawo okumala wiiki nga emu, era nga kafuna obulwadde okumala wiiki nga bbiri.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bannakyewa, abantu abalamu obulungi abafunye akawuka ka HCoV-229E baafuna obulwadde bwa ssennyiga omutono.
Abalwadde abatalina bulwadde buno batono nnyo abafunye obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu mputtu z'omukka.
Ekirwadde kya SARS, era ekimanyiddwa nga "ekirwadde kya pulomoniya ekitali kya bulijjo", kye kyaasooka mu byafaayo byonna eby'omuntu okuzuulibwa ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde ekireetebwa akawuka ka coronavirus, era ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV, akawuka ak'okusatu aka korona akazuulibwa ku bantu, kye kyaviirako.
Omulwadde wa SARS eyasooka yazuulibwa mu China mu Guangdong mu 2002
Mu kiseera kya SARS, abantu 8,096 be baakafuna obulwadde buno era abantu 774 be baafa, era obulwadde buno bwabuna mu nsi nnyingi ne mu nsi ezitali zimu.
Nga tetukwataganya abo abaasaasaanya obulwadde buno, kyabalirwa nti buli mulwadde asobola okussa abantu abalala nga babiri; ekiseera eky'okusiiga kyali wakati w'ennaku 4 ne 7, era omuwendo gw'abantu abaalina akawuka gwali ku lunaku olw'ekkumi.
Abalwadde abalina SARS-CoV, baatandika okuwulira obulumi mu mibiri, omutwe, omukka omungi, obulumi n'okutya, ate oluvannyuma ne bafuna obuwuka obw'amaanyi, okusukkirira n'okulemererwa okussa.
Ebintu ebitera okulemererwa mu by'okukozesa mu SARS kwe kulwala lymphopenia, obuzibu mu mputo n'okweyongera kwa creatine kinase.
Abalwadde ba SARS era balaba obuvune mu alveoli, obusavu bw'amasero ga epithelium n'okweyongera kw'omutindo gwa macrophages.
Abantu nga 20 oba 30 ku buli kikumi abafuna obulwadde buno beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi n'okufuuyira empewo.
Mu mbeera zino enzibu\ okuggyako mu mputtu z'omukka ez'omunda, ebitundu ebirala, omuli ekitundu ky'omukka gw'olubuto, ekibumba n'enso, bisobola okuyitibwa endwadde, nga kino kitera okuleetebwa sitokini, era kiyinza okutta abantu naddala abalwadde abalina obulwadde obw'omubiri.
Omusaayi guno gwasooka kuteekebwako mu biwundu bya muganda w'omulwadde eyava e Guangzhou n'ajja e Hong Kong.
Okuva olwo, waliwo ebikozesebwa bingi mu kunoonyereza ku kirwadde kya coronavirus.
Mu 2004 HCoV-NL63 yazuulibwa mu mwana ow'emyezi 7 okuva mu Netherlands.
Okusooka, kyazuulibwa nti kikwata ku baana abato, bannamukadde, n'abalwadde abalina obulwadde bw'omubiri n'obw'omukka.
Obulwadde obuleetebwa HCoV-NL63 buzingiramu obulwadde obuyitibwa cold, conjunctivitis, omusujja omungi, ne bronchiolitis.
Okunoonyereza okulala okw'obwannannyini kwalaga nti akawuka ako kaali kazuulibwa mu nnyindo z'omwana ow'emyezi 8 mu Netherlands eyalina obulwadde bw'amawuggwe.
Akawuka kazuulibwa mu Netherlands, naye mu butuufu kaabunye buli wamu.
Okusinziira ku kubala, HCoV-NL63 y'avunaanyizibwa ku bitundu 4,7% eby'endwadde z'omukka ez'enjawulo, era obulwadde obusookerwako bubaawo mu kiseera eky'ebbugumu, mu ttoggo ne mu biseera by'obutiti.
HCoV-NL63 ekwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bwa laryngitis obwa obstructive, era obuyitibwa obulwadde bwa grapefruit.
HCoV-HKU1 yalabikira mu Hong Kong mu mwaka ogwo okuva ku musajja ow'emyaka 71 eyali mu ddwaliro ng'alina omusujja gw'amawuggwe n'obulwadde bw'amaaso.
Ng'oggyeko omusujja gw'amawuggwe ogutava mu ddwaliro n'obulwadde bw'amaaso, HCoV-HKU1 ekwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bw'ekibumba.
Okufaananako HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43, akawuka ka HCoV-HKU1, akaviirako endwadde ez'omukka ez'omutindo omutono, kazuuliddwa mu nsi yonna.
