DATE/TIME Y'OKUSINZIIRA: 14 Ogwomunaana 2020, 00:24 UTC
OKUKKIRIZA: CC0: Obuyinza obukuumibwa tebuliiwo
Mu mwezi guno, tuli mu mbeera ya njawulo.
COVID-19 kye kizibu ekyakakasa engeri abantu gye banyumyako mu nsi yonna n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwe tulina eri bannaffe.
Tetulina bizibu ng'ebyo, naye tukimanyi nti engeri gye tukola obulungi byesigamye ku busobozi bw'okulaga obusaasizi, obumu n'okukulaakulanya ebibiina mu nsi yonna, nga bino bye bisinziirwako okukola.
Twalaba omukwano n'okulabirira wakati w'abakozi baffe bonna, nga kino kyeyolekera mu bubaka bwe twawuliziganya nabo ku ssimu, ku ssimu, ne mu mboozi - ekiraga nti tulina abantu ab'ekitalo.
Ndi musanyufu era nneenyumiriza nnyo okwogera ku mmwe ng'abakozi bannange.
Wiiki ewedde, nnawulira nga omulimu gwaffe gutenderezebwa nnyo.
Nzijukiziddwa obukulu bw'okufuna Wikipedia mu nsi yonna mu kiseera kino, era n'engeri buli muntu gy'ayinza okuganyulwa mu kuba n'enkola y'okufuna ensimbi eno ey'omuwendo ku mutimbagano.
Kino kisoboka olw'emirimu gyammwe, ka kibe nga kwe kukuuma emikutu gyaffe nga gikola, okusasula bakozi bannaffe, oba okukuuma obukuumi bw'ebitundu byaffe.
Ensi yeetaaga obubaka obuli mu Wikipedia, era kino kikulu nnyo leero okusinga bwe kyali kibadde.
Mu biseera nga bino, okusobola okufuna ebibala eby'omuganyulo mu nsi, si kye tukola kyokka ekikulu, naye n'engeri gye tukikola.
Olw'obukulu bw'omulimu guno n'ekifo kyammwe mu nkola eno, tujja kukola enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu ngeri gye tukolera awamu okutandika wiiki ejja.
Okukola ku Mitendera gy'Okukola n'Emirimu
Nga Robin bwe yategeezezza, ttiimu ya c-team yakuŋŋaana eggulo okukubaganya ebirowoozo ku ngeri gye tugenda okutambuzaamu emirimu gyaffe n'ebiseera eby'omu maaso.
Mu mboozi eyo, twekenneenya engeri gye tuyinza okukola obulungi mu mbeera eno era n'engeri y'okuyamba ekibiina kyaffe okusigala nga kivudde ku mbeera eyo.
Abasinga obungi ku ffe twali twagala okuggyawo obuzibu n'okunyweza omulimu gwaffe ogw'ekiseera kyonna.
Bw'oba oyagala okudda ennyuma, ka kibe bwe kityo.
Eri abakozi bonna, abakozi abapangisa n'abakozi abatali ba bulijjo:
Tusuubira nti abantu bano bajja kukolera essaawa nga nnya buli lunaku oba essaawa 20 buli wiiki okutuusa nga waliwo ekiragiro ekirala.
Tetutandika nnaku za kuwummula: singa osobola okukola essaawa ezisingawo, ekyo kisoboka olw'ekigendererwa kyaffe.
Kyokka, ensi eno tetegerekeka; ka kibe nti ebyetaago byo bye biruwa, ka bibe kulabirira ba ŋŋanda zo, kugula mmere, oba okugenda okulaba omusawo, obukuumi bwo kye kintu kye tukulembeza.
Tetukwata biseera byammwe bya mulimu.
Bw'oba oli mulwadde, tolina kukola.
Kino kitegeerekeka bulungi era tekiriimu kubuusabuusa, naye tukyogerako.
Tekikwetaagisa kuwandiisa layisinsi oba okuwummulako, wabula buulira omukulu wo era oyambe ekibiina okukyusa kalenda n'enteekateeka z'emirimu okusobola okulaba nti ebitundu ebikulu bikuumibwa.
(Bw'oba olina obulwadde bwa COVID-19, tuukirira Brian owa T&C Ops asobole okuwa T&C obuyambi n'okukuuma embeera yo).
Ssente ez'essaawa zonna zijja kusasulwa.
Twamala dda okulangirira era ne tukakasa nti twagala okutuukiriza obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe eri abakozi baffe n'abapangisa nga tusasulwa essaawa.
Buli muntu ajja kusasulwa okusinziira ku misolo gy'essaawa egikolerwako mu mbeera eza bulijjo.
Kino kizingiramu ebiseera by'obulwa obulwadde bw'osobola okukola.
Bw'oba oyagala okukola, tujja kukuyamba.
Abantu bangi bakozesa emirimu gyabwe okuteeka essira ku nsi etwetoolodde.
Ekyo kye tukola kiyinza okuvaamu ebirungi, naddala mu biseera ng'ebyo.
Era nate, kino kyetaagisa okweyamba.
Tukusaba oyogere n'omukulu wo tusobole okumanya by'olina okusuubira era tusobole okukola enkyukakyuka mu ngeri esaanira.
Emirimu egimu gitwalibwa okuba emikulu.
Ebintu ng'ebyo tusaanidde okubiwagira.
Ebibiina bya SRE, HR Ops, Trust&Safety ne Fundraising (nga n'ebirala) birina emirimu emikulu gye bakola era nga giyinza okwetaaga obuyambi obulala.
Twatandikawo enkola mu bitongole byonna okutunula ku biruubirirwa byaffe ebikyaliwo n'okussa essira ku kuwa obuyambi obwetaagisa mu mulimu gwaffe.
Waliwo emirimu mingi buli omu gy'alina okukola, era essira tulitadde ku mirimu egisinga obukulu.
Okwewola leero tekitegeeza nti ojja kufuna ebizibu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Tetusuubira kukola mirundi ebiri okusobola okuzzaawo ebyo bye twafiirwa oluvannyuma lw'ekikangabwa.
Tojja kukolera biseera bisukka ku ebyo by'obadde oyagala okusobola okutuukiriza ebisaanyizo by'ekiseera kino.
Tukimanyi nti embeera zikyuse, era tujja kukola ku kutuulawo ebiruubirirwa ebipya n'ebiseera eby'enkomerero, bwe kiba kisoboka.
Kiki ekituuka ku APP (enteekateeka z'omwaka)?
Okutuukana n'ebiseera ebikyuse n'ebisuubirwa ku bungi bw'ekiseera ky'okukolera, tugenda kukyusa ebiseera by'okutuukiriza Enteekateeka yaffe ey'Omwaka 2020-2021.
Tusuubira okuteekawo ekiseera eky'okuddamu mu nteekateeka yaffe eya 2019-2020, nga kino kiwa abakozi ebiseera ebisingawo okukola embalirira, kibasobozese okukulembeza emirimu gyabwe egy'omugaso, okweyambisa n'okulabirira abaagalwa baabwe, nga buli muntu yenna eyeetaaga oba ayagala okukola aweebwa essaawa entono ez'okukola mu wiiki eziddako.
Okweyongera mu biseera kino kiyamba okukendeeza ennyo ku buzibu obuli mu nteekateeka n'obutebenkevu mu kibiina.
Wiiki ejja tujja kuteekawo ekiteeso kyaffe eri akakiiko, nga tutegeeza abakiise n'ebibinja ku kya kukola amangu ddala nga tukakasizza.
Tumwebaza APP olw'okukulembera omulimu guno.
Embeera y'omu ofiisi, akabi, n'okulongoosa
Wiiki ewedde, twakizuula nti omu ku bakozi bannaffe mu San Francisco ayinza okuba ng'alina akawuka ka COVID-19.
Kyokka, ng'oggyeko okukola ebintu ebirala, twasalawo okupangisa ekibinja ky'abazigu okuyonja ebifo byonna mu ofiisi yaffe mu San Francisco.
Baakozesa eddagala erigema akawuka okusaanyaawo ebifo byonna, awamu n'ebisenge eby'okwaniriza abantu n'eby'okusitula abantu okuva we batuuka ku mwaliiro gwaffe.
Ekizimbe kirina amateeka gaakyo ag'obwegendereza, nga kikozesa ebintu ebikuuma abapangisa baabwe nga balamu bulungi.
Tulowooza nti ofiisi eno ejja kuba etegese bulungi mu kiseera kye tunaakomawo.
Ofiisi yaffe mu DC eri ku mukutu gwa WeWork, ogwatusanga n'abakozi bonna mu DC, ku mateeka gaayo agakwata ku COVID-19.
Wiiki ewedde, ofiisi yaffe mu Disitulikiti ya Columbia yakyusibwa n'egenda ku mikutu gyaffe nga bwe kiragiddwa mu San Francisco.
Nga bwe mukimanyi, abamu ku bakozi bannaffe mu New York, twogera ne ku nsonga y'okusasula ennyumba mu Brooklyn.
Enkyukakyuka ng'ezo zikyagenda mu maaso, naye zisobola okuteekebwawo.
Abamu ku bakozi bannaffe guno gwe mulundi gwabwe ogusoose okukola nga bali wala.
Bakkiriza bannaffe ab'edda abakola ku mikutu emirala bamanyi nti waliwo engeri gye tuyinza okukyusaamu, era baagala okuwa amagezi:
Kikkirizibwa okukendeeza ku budde bw'enkuŋŋaana okutuuka ku ssaawa emu oba bbiri.
Bw'oba weetaaga okusomera okumala ekiseera ekiwanvu, lowooza ku ngeri gy'oyinza okugabamu amasomero go.
Manya ekigendererwa ky'olukuŋŋaana, olukuŋŋaana lwo, era omutume ebintu by'olina okubuulirako abalala nga bukyali.
Kozesa vidiyo ng'ekisanja, era kozesa ebintu nga Google Docs ne Zoom okusobola okukolagana obulungi.
Okutuusa kati, osobola okuteekawo omuteesiteesi  omuntu anaakebera ebibuuzo ebijja mu mboozi n'okulabirira olukalala lw'abo abanaayogera, era n'oyo avunaanyizibwa ku kukuba ebiwandiiko (oba okubikkula awamu).
Bw'oba oyagala okukozesa ekikozesebwa mu kuwulira, tuukirira obuyambi ku e-mail.
Kozesa omukisa gwo ogwa Wellness Reimbursement ng'ogula ebyokulya.
Yingira ku Slack #remoties channel oyogere ne bakozi banno ku mirimu egy'okugabana.
Ekibinja kya HR Operations kyekenneenya ebitabo ebikubibwa mu ngeri ya webinar okusobola okuyamba ekibiina kyonna okukola obulungi emirimu.
Wiiki ewedde, twasaba bonna abafuna ssente okuva mu kibiina okuggyawo ebikujjuko ebikozesebwa Wikimedia, nga editathons, okutuusa nga WHO ekirangiridde nti kawumpuli aggwa.
Tukitegeera era tutegeeza nti okusaba kwaffe okw'okuggyawo ebiragiro bino n'ebirala ebiyinza okulemesa enteekateeka z'ensimbi okutuukirizibwa, era tewali ajja kusasulwa olw'okumala ebiseera bingi oba okukyusa ebigendererwa ebyo.
Mu wiiki ejja tujja kukubiriza ebitundu ebirala eby'okuyiga ebikwata ku Wikimania, wamu n'enkuŋŋaana endala ez'ebitundu n'ez'ebitundu.
Embeera y'ensi yonna  tekiri nti abantu banakuwavu olw'okulekera awo okukola naye era waliwo obuweerero olw'okutegeera obulungi n'okubeera n'enkizo ey'okudda mu bitundu byabwe, ku Wikimedia n'ebirala.
Ku nsonga y'okwetegereza, CRT ekola ku lupapula mu Meta-Wiki olujja okuwa ekifo ekirimu abantu ab'enjawulo okulabirira n'okunyumya.
Tubeera mu kakwate ku nsonga ezikwata ku COVID-19
Tujja kusindika akawayiro k'okuyita abantu mu lukuŋŋaana olw'enjawulo olujja okubaawo ku Lwokuna, ku ssaawa 2:00 UTC/07:00 PT.
Ku luno tugenda kukozesa omukisa guno okugabana obubaka obupya, okuddamu ebibuuzo byammwe, era tubeereko wamu nga tunyumya.
Tuli wamu mu mbeera eno era tuli beetegefu okuyamba mu ngeri yonna gye tusobola.
Wadde kiri kityo, osobola okufuna obubaka okuva mu bubaka buno, era n'ebirala ebikulu ebikwata ku COVID-19  okuva ku Office Wiki.
CRT ejja kuddamu okufulumya empapula ng'ezo era obubaka bwonna bujja kukuŋŋaanyizibwa mu kifo kimu.
Era tukola ku kukuuma enkolagana n'abakozi abali mu nsi ezikoseddwa ennyo embeera eno.
Bw'oba olina ebibuuzo ebikwata ku ntambula, ebikujjuko, emirimu, ebizibu mu kubuulira oba bw'oba weetaaga obuyambi ojja kufuna obuyambi okuva mu CRT.
Tuli beetegefu okuwa obuyambi n'okuwuliziganya nga bwe kiba kyetaagisa.
Bw'oba olina ekizibu kyonna ekikwata ku bwama, tuukirira Brian Judan, akulira HR International Global Operations.
Enkyukakyuka ng'ezo tezaalina kutwalibwa ng'okulagajjalira obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe.
Wabula, kyawukana: kwe kukkiriza nti waliwo obwetaavu obw'okuddamu okukola emirimu gyaffe n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe.
Tukkiriza nti ebintu ng'ebyo byetaagisa okusobola okuwagana n'okutuusa omulimu gwaffe ku ntandikwa, okuwagira ekibiina kyaffe n'ensi yonna nga tubawa obuyambi obwetaagisa.
