Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme ekwataganyizibwa n'ebitundu by'omubiri eby'omu mawuggwe, emisulo gy'omutima, ensigo n'ebisenge.
ACE2 evuganya ebikolwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ekikwatagana nayo, nga kikendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin-II era nga kyongera ku Ang (1-7), nga kino kifuula ekkubo eryasuubizibwa ery'okujjanjaba endwadde z'omutima. AC2 era ekola ng'ekifo eky'okuyingira mu bulago bwa koronavaayirasi ezimu.
Enzimu ey'omu bantu eyitibwa hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2  ensimbi erimu zinki eri ku maaso g'ensulo za endothelial n'endala.
ACE2 protein erimu N-end peptidaze domain M2 ne C-end transport domain ey'ekisenge kya amino acid colectrin.
ACE2 ye protein eya membrane eya type I, erina enzyme ey'amaanyi era erina ekitundu ekikwata ku bitundu by'omubiri ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ACE2 ekitali kya mu nseke kiwandikawo okuva ku kitundu kya transmembrane ne ekirala ekimanyiddwa nga sheddaze, era obutoffaali obuvunda bufuluma mu musaayi era ne bufuluma ne mu nsawo.
ACE2 eri mu bitundu ebisinga: ACE2 esimbiddwa ku lususu lw'ensulo ez'ensulo ez'ensulo ez'omu bungi ez'omu lubuto ez'engeri II, enterocyte ez'omubiri omutono, ensala z'omubiri ez'omu nsalo n'ez'omu nsalo, n'ensalo z'omubiri ez'omu nsalo ez'omu bungi.
ACE2 ne RNA biyosenteesi era ezisangibwa mu bwongo, mu striatum, mu hypothalamus ne mu bwongo.
Omulimu omukulu ogwa ACE2 kwe kukola ng'omuzigo gwa ACE.
ACE esobola okuvvuunuka akawuka akayitibwa angiotensin I ne kafuuka angiotensin II.
ACE2, mu ngeri ye, ekwata ku carboxyl amino acid ey'enkomerero eya phenylalanine okuva ku angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era n'egikendeeza ne gifuuka angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 era esobola okusalako peptide endala ezitali zimu, omuli [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era ekakasa enkola y'okuyisa mu lususu eya SLC6A19 era eriwo mu bulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'ekimera ekirimu ekitundu ekimu eky'omubiri, ACE2 y'esobola okuyingira mu butoffaali bwa koronavirusi ezimu, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akaviirako SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akaviirako COVID-19).
Mu bufunze, okukwata protein S1 eya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ku ACE2 ku lususu lw'ensulo kiviirako endocytosis n'okuyingiza akawuka ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu nsolo.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa protein S okuteekebwawo serine protease ey'omutunzi TMPRSS2, okuziyiza kwe kati kwe kunoonyerezaako ng'obujjanjabi obwesigika. Kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2 mu bulabe bw'obulwadde buno kiyinza okuyamba okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Wadde kiri kityo, ebibiina bingi eby'emikono n'abakulembeze b'emisango bakubiriza abantu okweyongera okukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa ACE inhibitor ne BRA.
