Enkola za COVID-19 ze programu za ssimu ezikozesebwa okuyamba mu kunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe mu 2019-20, kwe kugamba, okumanya abantu (abo abaabadde n'obulwadde) abaabadde n'omuntu alina obulwadde.
Mu bitundu ebimu, waliwo enkola nnyingi ezikozesebwa mu butongole ezikoleddwa oba ezaaweebwa.
Waliwo enkola ez'enjawulo ezikozesebwa mu kunoonyereza ku bantu.
Kino kyaleetawo empaka ku nsonga z'obwannannyini naddala ku nkola ezisinziira ku kulabirira ebifo abantu we babeera.
Enkola endala ez'ekisajja mu nsonga eno, kwe kukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ku ssimu endala.
Nga 10 April, 2020, Google ne Apple baalangirira nti bajja kukolera wamu okuteekawo programu ez'okuweereza nga Bluetooth mu nkola zaabwe ez'okuweereza Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti awamu ne Alipay batandisewo programu esobozesa abantu okukebera oba nga baatuukiddwako abantu abalina COVID-19.
Era ekozesebwa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 mu China. Mu Singapore, waliwo programu eyitibwa TraceTogether.
Ekitongole kya Gavumenti ekikola ku by'okwerinda mu ggwanga ekya North Macedonia kitandisewo programu ya StopKorona! ekozesa Bluetooth okuyamba abantu okumanya abantu abalina obulwadde buno era n'okuwuliziganya n'ab'obuyinza.
App eno yateekebwawo minisitule y'eby'empuliziganya n'entambula n'ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu.
Nga 14 April 2020, app yali esembedde okuwandiisibwa mu Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga April 12, gavumenti yategeeza nti programu y'okukebera abantu eri mu mitendera egy'enkomerero era ejja kuba eriwo mu wiiki eziwerako.
Australia ne New Zealand zirowooza ku kukozesa programu eziriko TraceTogether eya Singapore ne BlueTrace protocol. Russia eteekateeka okukozesa programu ey'okuteeka ebifo mu bifo eby'enjawulo, ekigendererwa kyaayo kwe kukakasa nti abalwadde abalina COVID-19 ababeera mu Moscow tebasimbula maka gaabwe.
Ross Anderson, profesa mu byokwerinda, mu yunivasite ya Cambridge, alaga ebizibu bingi ebiyinza okuva mu nkola ez'okuteekawo enkola ez'okuweereza, nga mw'otwalidde okuteekawo enkola ez'obulimba n'obutaba na busobozi bw'okuteekawo enkola ng'abantu batono nnyo be bagikozesa.
Olw'okweraliikirira nti programu ez'akabi ez'akabi ez'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe (coronavirus) ziyinza okusaasaana, Apple yakendeeza ku bika by'ebibiina ebiyinza okuwaayo programu ezikwata ku ssenyiga omukambwe (coronavirus) ku App Store, nga ziwa ebibiina ebikakafu (official) oba ebirala byokka.
Google ne Amazon nabyo byaliko ekkomo.
Ab'empaka ez'obukuumi baalaga nti beeraliikirivu olw'ebyo ebiyinza okuva mu kulaba abantu nga bakozesa programu ezikwata ku ssenyiga omukambwe; naddala, ekibuuzo ky'okuba nti enkola y'okwetegereza eyagambibwa okulwanyisa ssenyiga omukambwe ejja kuggibwawo ng'akabi kagenze.
Ekibiina kya Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisukka mu 100 bafulumizza ekiteeso nga basaba okukomya okulabirira abantu ng'abo.
Ebibiina byalangiridde embeera munaana ze biwa ku pulojekiti z'eggwanga:
okwetegereza kulina kuba kwa mateeka, kwetaagisa era kwa bwenkanya;
okwongera ku kulabirira n 'okukebera kulina okuleetebwaako okuteeka ekkomo ku kiseera eky ' okukoleramu;
okukozesa obubaka kulina kuba kukomye mu kulwanyisa COVID-19;
Obukuumi n'obutegeerekeka bw'ebikwata ku bantu birina okukuumibwa era n'obukakafu bw'obukuumi obwo bulina okuweebwa.
okwetegereza okw 'omulembe kulina okulemesa abantu okusosolwa n 'okusuulibwa ku ludda olulala;
okussaamu kwonna kw'ebikwata ku bantu ab'okusatu kulina kuba kuteekeddwa ku mutindo gwa mateeka;
Obukuumi okuva ku kukozesa obubi, era n'eddembe ly'abantu okuddamu ku kukozesa obubi, birina okukakasibwa.
Kikulu nnyo okuteekawo  okuyingira mu ngeri ey'omugaso  okwa bonna  abakwatibwako, omuli abakugu mu by'obulamu n'abakiikirira ebibinja ebirese abantu ku bunkenke.
Google ne Apple bataddewo enteekateeka yaabwe ey'okuggyawo obuzibu bw'okwetegereza obutayosa, nga kino kizingiramu okuggya enkola y'okukebera mu nkola z'ebyuma byabwe nga tezikyetaagisa.
Mu nsi ezimu, mu kifo ky'okukozesa programu, bakozesa enkola ey'okuzuula ebifo, ekikendeeza ku ky'okukozesa programu n'okulemererwa okugoberera.
Mu Isiraeri, okulondoola kwa mu Internet kukkiriziddwa.
Enkola z'oku mutimbagano ezirina ensibuko y'obubaka ku kifo nazo zirina obuzibu bwa buwandiike.
Kyokka, si buli nkola erina abaweereza abakulu nti erina okuba n'okufuna obubaka ku kifo omuntu gy'ali; waliwo enkola ezimu ezikoleddwa nga tezikwata ku muntu yenna, nga zikozesa abaweereza abakulu okuwuliziganya bokka (laba akatundu ak'okudda wansi).
Mu South Korea, enkola ey'okunoonyereza ku bantu yakozesebwa nga tewakozesa programu.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa programu, enkola eno yakuŋŋaanya obubaka okuva mu nsi ezitali zimu, omuli obubaka obuva ku ssimu n'obwa kaadi, n'ebikwataganya okufulumya obubaka ku bantu abayinza okuba nga balina obulwadde.
Gavumenti teyakozesa bubaka buno kubuulirira bantu ku bantu abayinza okuba nga beenyigidde mu bulwadde buno kyokka, naye era n'okufuula obubaka ku kifo we bali obutuuka ku bantu bonna, nga kino kisobose olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu mateeka agakwata ku kukuuma obubaka ezaakolebwa oluvannyuma lw'obulwadde bwa MERS mu ggwanga lino.
Amawanga, omuli ne Bugirimaani, gatunuulira enkola ez'okukozesa enkola ez'okuteekawo n'ez'okukuuma ebyama.
Nga 6 April 2020, ebintu ebirala tebinnaba kutegeerekeka.
Okuzuula abantu nga bakuuma ebyama  kye kigendererwa ekimanyiddwa obulungi, ekirimu ebitabo bingi eby'okunoonyereza okuva mu 2013.
Kyokka, PEPP-PT kye kivudde mu kukolagana okulimu enkola ez'enjawulo, nga kuliko n'ezo ez'obwannannyini era nga tezirina nkola emu. Enkola ez'obwannannyini zirimu enkola ey'obwannannyini ey'obwannannyini ey'obwannannyini (DP-PPT/DP-3T), ennamba ez'ekiseera (TCN, fka Contact EventNumbers, CEN), enkola ez'obwannannyini, enkola ez'okunoonyereza ku mikwano gya ssimu (PACT), n'endala.
Enkola zino ze zaavanga ziyamba okulaba nti obubaka obukwata ku muntu tebuva ku kyuma, era nti byonna ebifaanagana bikolebwa ku kyuma.
The Privacy Group, MIT Media Lab ekola ku SafePaths, ekitebe ekikuuma obukuumi bw'obuntu nga kikuŋŋaanya era nga kikozesa obubaka bw'ekifo oba obw'okuyita mu kkubo okunoonyereza ku kusaasaana kwa COVID-19.
Omulimu gwa pulatifoomu eno gwesigamiziddwa ku kunoonyereza okuleeteddwa mu kiwandiiko Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic (Apps-goons: How to keep privacy in an Epidemic), ekyafulumizibwa mu March 2020. Omulimu omulala oguli mu ngeri y'emu gwe SafeTrace platform, eyakolebwa Enigma MPC, kkampuni ekola ku tekinologiya w'obukuumi era nga nayo yasooka kutandikibwawo MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya omunywevu ogusobozesa abakozesa okugabana obubaka obw'obumativu ku kifo we bali n'embeera y'obulamu bwabwe n'abakozesa abalala n'abakungu nga tebasse bwesige mu bubaka obwo.
Nga 5 April, 2020, ebibinja ebirina endowooza y'emu era nga bikozesa enkola ezifaanagana, byatandikawo ekibiina kya TCN Global Coalition, ekigendererwa kyakyo kwe kukendeeza ku kusattulukuka n'okukuuma obumu bw'ensi yonna mu nkola z'okukebera n'okulangirira, ekikulu mu kubunyisa.
Nga 9 April, 2020, gavumenti ya Singapore yalangirira nti yali evuddeyo ku code ya BlueTrace ekozesebwa mu nkola yaayo.
Nga 10 April, 2020, Google ne Apple, kampuni ezifuga ebyuma bya Android ne iOS, zaalangirira enteekateeka y'okunoonyereza ku bantu, ze bagamba nti zijja kukuuma ebyama, era nga zisinziira ku kukozesa tekinologiya wa Bluetooth Low Energy n'okuteekawo enkola ey'okuteeka obubaka ku mutimbagano.
Era baafulumya n'obubonero bw'obukodyo obw'obukodyo obukozesebwa mu nkola eno.
Okusinziira ku Apple ne Google, enkola eno erina okuteekebwawo mu mitendera esatu:
okutandikawo ebyuma ebikkiriza gavumenti okukola programu ez'obuyinza okukebera abantu abalina akawuka ka coronavirus, kyokka nga tezikakasa bya buwandiike
Nga bagatta ekitundu kino mu iOS ne Android, Google ne Apple bateekateeka okugonjoola ebizibu eby'okwetegereza obutayosa, okusooka nga batandikawo enkola nga bayita mu kuzza obuggya enkola y'okusindika obubaka, oluvannyuma ne bagiggyawo mu ngeri y'emu ng'obutebenkevu bumaze okuggwaawo.
Okuteeka eddagala mu kifo ekirala (era amanyiddwa nga okudda mu mbeera, okudda mu mbeera endala, okukyusa ekigendererwa, oba okudda mu mbeera endala) kwe kuddamu okutwala eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba obulwadde oba embeera ey'ekisawo ey'enjawulo ku eyo eyasooka okuteekebwawo.
Kino kye kimu ku bintu eby'okunoonyereza ebikozesebwa mu kiseera kino okuteekawo obujjanjabi obumatiza era obwangu mu COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza okulala kuzingiramu okukola eddagala erigema COVID-19 n'okuteekebwamu plasma. SARS-CoV-2 erimu obutoffaali nga 66 obuyinza okukwatibwako eddagala, nga buli bumu buliko ebifo ebiwerako ebinyweza ligand.
Okunoonyereza ku bitundu bino ebinyweza obuwuka buyamba mu kufulumya eddagala erigenda okuziyiza obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obuyitibwa papain-like protease, RNA-dependent RNA-polymerase, helicase, protein S ne ADF-ribophosphataze, bye bintu ebikulu ennyo ebirina okukozesebwa.
Hussein AA ne banne mu kunoonyereza kwabwe okwasooka, beekenneenya eddagala erimu eryali lisobola okukozesebwa, ne balongoosaamu, era ne banoonyereza ku ngeri gye lifaananamu n'eddagala eryasembayo okukkirizibwa, okusobola okwanguya okukulaakulanya eddagala erikola obulungi erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 eryandibadde lisobola okukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza.
Chloroquine ddagala erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri era lirina ebikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bw'endwadde ezimu ez'obutafa.
Nga 18 omwezi guno ogwa March, WHO yalangirira nti chlorokine ne hydroxychloroquine ezirimu zijja kubaamu eddagala erina okunoonyereza ku kkolera lya "Solidarity".
Gavana wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okunoonyereza ku chlorokine ne hydroxychloroquine kujja kutandika mu ssaza lya New York nga March 24. Nga March 28, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne chlorokine phosphate okusinziira ku lukusa lwayo olw'amangu (EUA).
Ekirwadde kino tekikkirizibwa mu nkola ya FDA ey'okugezesebwa mu ddwaaliro era kikkirizibwa wansi wa EUA ng'eddagala ery'okugezesa lyokka eri abalwadde abali mu ddwaliro naye nga tebasobola kufuna bujjanjabi mu bikolwa bya ddwaaliro.
CDC egamba nti enkola y'okukozesa, eddagala oba ebbanga ly'okukozesa hydroxychloroquine okutangira oba okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 tekinnategeerekeka.
Abasawo bagamba nti bakozesa eddagala nga tebalina kya kwekolera.
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza mu Turkey mu Istanbul, kikoze okunoonyereza okutono ku kukozesa chlorokine ng'ekozesebwa awamu ne zinc ne vitamin A, C ne D.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi kukolebwa mu yunivasite ya Duke ne Oxford.
Essomero ly'eby'obujjanjabi mu Yunivasite y'e New York mu Langon liyiga ku bukuumi n'obuwanguzi bw'okukozesa eddagala eriyitibwa hydroxychloroquine.
Okugezesebwa mu China mu Wuhan ne Shenzhen kwalaga nti favipiravir yali ya mugaso nnyo.
Abalwadde 35 mu Shenzhen abaafuna eddagala lino bafunye obuzibu mu nnaku 4 nga bwe bali, ate abalwadde 45 abataafuna ddagala lino bafunye obulwadde okumala ennaku 11.
Mu Wuhan, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa kulabye abalwadde 240 abalina omusujja gw'amawuggwe, ekitundu kimu kyaweebwa favipiravir ate ekitundu ekirala kyaweebwa umifenvir.
Ekitongole ky'eddagala ekya Italy kyajjukiza abantu nti ebivudde mu kunoonyereza ku ddagala lino bitono era tebisaanidde kutwalibwa ng'ebituufu.
Nga 2 omwezi gwa Apuli, Bugirimaani yalangirira nti ejja kugula eddagala mu Japan okuzzaawo ebirungo byayo, era nti ejja kukozesa eby'obufuzi by'amagye okulitwala mu malwaliro ga yunivasite, awali eddagala erigenda okukozesebwa okujjanjaba abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Okusinziira ku lupapula lw'amawulire oluyitibwa South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yategeezezza gavumenti ya Trump nti eddagala eryo liyinza okuba nga terikola bulungi ku bantu abalina obulwadde buno.
Okukozesa eddagala lino kiyinza obutaba kya bukuumi eri abalwadde abali embuto oba abalwadde abagezaako okufuna olubuto.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku ddagala eriyitibwa lopiinavir n'eryitibwa ritonavir (Kaletra) kwalaga nti eddagala eryo teryali ddungi.
Eddagala lino lyakolebwa okuziyiza okwekulaakulanya kwa HIV nga ligatta ku protease.
