Okusinziira ku kiwandiiko ekyafulumizibwa ekitongole kya WHO, olunaku luno lwe December 8, 2019.
Okutwalira awamu, waliwo enkola ezitali zimu ezikozesebwa okubalirira okufa.
Ebimu ku bintu ebireetera abantu okukwatibwa obulwadde buno kwe kuba nti abantu bangi bakeberebwa, obulwadde buno bulwadde bwa maanyi, obulwadde buno bulwadde bwa maanyi, obulwadde buno bulwadde bwa maanyi nnyo, era abantu bangi balina obulwadde buno.
Mu nkomerero ya 2019, WHO yawa ekirwadde koodi z'obudde obw'amangu ku ICD-10: U07.1  ku kufa okuva ku bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obwasangibwa mu laboratory ne U07.2  ku kufa okuva ku COVID-19 eyazuulibwa mu ddwaliro oba ku bulwadde bw'abantu nga tewali bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obwasangibwa mu laboratory.
Okusinziira ku kiwandiiko kya Yunivasite ya Johns Hopkins, nga 17 Apuli 2020, omuwendo gw'abantu abafa n'abalwadde ku nsi yonna gwali 6,9% (153 822/2 240 191).
Omuwendo guno gukyuka okusinziira ku kitundu. Engeri endala ezimu kuliko okusalawo kw'omugaso gw'okufa kw'obulwadde (CFR), ekiraga omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa nga bafudde obulwadde, era n'okusalawo kw'omugaso gw'okufa kw'obulwadde (IFR), ekiraga omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa (abazuuliddwa n'abatazuuliddwa) abafudde obulwadde.
Ebikwata ku bantu bano tebitegekeddwa ku kiseera kya njawulo era biraga abantu abawerako okuva lwe baakafuna obulwadde okutuuka lwe baamala.
Wadde ng'abantu abamu abafunye obulwadde buno tebabaako bulwadde bwonna obubaleetera okulwanyisa, bwe baba nga baliko obuwuka obwo, kisobola okuyamba omuntu okumanya abantu bameka abafunye obulwadde obwo.
Mu kibuga ky'e Italy, Castiglione d'Adda, ekyalo ekirina abantu 4,600, abantu 80 (1,7%) tebakyali balamu.
Mu kibuga Gangelt, obulwadde bwabuna wakati mu bavubuka nga bakuza embaga ya carnival, nga buviirako okufa okutono, era si buli muntu eyafa COVID-19 nti yali asobola okuyitibwa ng'afudde.
Ate era, embeera y'obulamu mu Bugirimaani yali teyeeraliikiriza nnyo.
Mu Netherlands abantu nga 3 ku buli kikumi bayinza okuba n'omubiri ogusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde buno okusinziira ku musaayi oguweebwayo.
COVID-19  y'ensonga entongole ey'abantu 69 abafudde (0,004% ku bantu).
Obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino n'omuwendo gw'abafa byawukana ku basajja n'abakazi.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu China ne Italy, abasajja be basinga okufa.
Ekibinja ekisinga okuba mu kabi  abasajja abali mu myaka 50 n'okusingawo; enjawulo wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi ekendeera okuva ku myaka 90 gyokka.
Mu China, omuwendo gw'abafu gwali gwa bitundu 2.8 ku buli kikumi ku basajja n'ebitundu 1.7 ku buli kikumi ku bakazi.
Ensonga eziviirako enjawulo eyo tezimanyiddwa, naye ziyinza okuba nga za mu buzaale oba mu nneeyisa.
Enjawulo mu by'obujjanjabi wakati w'ekikula, okunywa ssigala okutono mu bakazi, endwadde ez'omunda mu basajja (ng'omusaayi omungi oguba mu basajja nga bakyali bato okusinga mu bakazi) biyinza okuba nga bye bireetera abasajja okufa.
Mu Bulaaya, 57% ku bantu abaakafuna obulwadde buno baali basajja, era 72% ku bantu abaafa COVID-19 baali basajja.
Okutuusa mu Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Amerika teriiko kubala kwa basajja na bakazi ku COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti endwadde ez'obulabe gamba nga Ebola, HIV, ekikulukuto, ne ssenyiga omukambwe zirina ebitundu eby'enjawulo eby'obusajja.
Abakyala be basinga okukola mu by'obulamu naddala abasawo, era nga kino kibaleetera okufuna obulwadde buno.
Nga 11 Febwali 2020, ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu ekya World Health Organization kyalangirira erinnya ly'ekirwadde kino nga  COVID-19.
Akulira ekitongole kya WHO, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, annyonnyola: CO kitegeeza kiroona, VI  akawuka, D  obulwadde, era 19  omwaka ekirwadde kino lwe kyasoose okweyoleka: 31 December 2019.
Erinnya lino lyalondebwa okwewala okwogerako ku kifo ekimu (ng'ekyokulabirako, China), ebika by'ebisolo, oba ebibinja by'abantu nga bwe kyetaagisa mu kubuulirira kw'ensi yonna okukwata ku kuyitibwa, okweggyako okuswala.
Mu bubaka bw'abantu bonna, WHO ekozesa ebigambo akawuka ka COVID-19 ne akawuka akaviirako COVID-19.
Obulwadde n'akawuka byombi biyitibwa "coronavirus".
Mu kiseera eky'okusaasaana okwasooka mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byayitibwanga coronavirus ne Wuhannian coronavirus.
Mu January 2020, okusinziira ku kubuulirira kwa 2015 okukwata ku kukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'endwadde ne virus, WHO yasalawo okukozesa ebigambo Acute respiratory disease 2019-nCov ne 2019-nCoV ng'amannya ag'akaseera ag'akawuka n'endwadde.
Nga 11 February, 2020, amannya ag'obuwandiike gaafulumizibwa  COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2.
Olw'obutaba na busobozi bwa maanyi mu nkola y'okugaba, abafulumya ebintu ebimu ebiba bifulumidde ku Intaneeti bakozesa ebintu eby'ekisawo, gamba ng'ebikozesebwa mu kutwala obuwuka obuyitibwa IVR.
Mu mbeera emu, eddwaliro ly'omu Italy lyali lyetaaga nnyo ekikopo ky'amazzi, era ng'omuweesi waakyo tasobola kukituusa mu kiseera kye yali ayagala, era omu ku bakugu baayo yaddamu okukola ekikopo ekyo era n'asobola okukuba ekikopo ekyo mu kiro kimu.
Okuva COVID-19 lwe yatandika okusaasaana, endowooza ez'obulimba, obubaka obutali bwa mazima n'obw'obulimba ku nsibuko ya kawuka, omuwendo gwaako, okutangira, okujjanjaba n'ebirala, byatandika okusaasaana ku Internet.
Kirabika abantu basobola okuleeta akawuka ku bisolo ebirala.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza tebikkiriziganyizza na busaasaanyizi bwa kirwadde kino mu mbizzi, ebinazi n'enkoko.
Mu kiseera kino tewali ddagala erikkirizibwa erigema akawuka kano oba eddagala erigakolako.
Mu kiseera kino, ebibiina bya gavumenti, ebibinja by'abayizi n'abanoonyereza mu mitendera gyonna bakola okunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa COVID-19 n'eddagala.
Mu March, WHO yatandikawo programu eyitibwa SOLIDARITY Trial, era ekigendererwa kyayo kwe kulaba engeri eddagala eryo gye liyinza okujjanjaba abantu abana.
Tewali ddagala likomekkerezebwa, naye ebibiina ebitali bimu bikolera ku ddagala erigenda okuteekebwamu eddagala.
SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 zombi ziyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu nga bikozesa ACE2 receptor, n'olwekyo, okunoonyereza ku SARS-CoV okwasooka kukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza.
Waliwo enkola ssatu ez'okulwanyisa obulwadde buno.
Ekisooka, abanoonyereza baagala okuteekawo eddagala eririna obusa.
Okukozesa akawuka kano, ka kube nga tekakolebwako oba nga tekakyaliwo, kigendererwa kya kuleetawo okwanukula okw'omubiri okw'amangu ku bulwadde obuppya bwa COVID-19.
Enkola ey'okubiri, okuteekawo eddagala eririna ekitundu ekimu, kwe kuteekawo eddagala eriyamba obulwadde obw'omubiri okukwata ekitundu ekimu eky'akawuka.
Mu mbeera ya SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza ng'okwo kulina ekigendererwa eky'okumalawo protein eya S-spike, eyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE2 receptor.
Enkola eyokusatu  kwe kukola eddagala eryesigamiziddwa ku nucleic acids (DNA oba RNA vaccine, enkola empya ey'okufuula eddagala).
Okugezaako okulwanyisa obulwadde buno kutegekeddwa okukeberebwa ku bukuumi n'obwanguzi. Ku Lwakuna nga 16, 2020, okusooka okunoonyereza ku bulwadde buno ku bantu bana kwatandika mu Seattle.
Ekirwadde kino kiva ku bulwadde obuyitibwa SARS-COV-2 era nga kirina enkola yaakyo ey'obutonde ey'obutonde.
Okutuusa mu Apuli 2020, waliwo okugezesebwa kwa ddwaaliro okusukka mu 300.
Eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba omusujja gw'ensiri lyali lirina okunoonyereza omusanvu, era okunoonyereza kwa mirundi ena kwali ku hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Okuddaabiriza eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka k'omusujja ku mubiri kye kisinga okuteekawo okunoonyereza mu China; ku nkomerero ya Apuli, mu nsi eziwerako, okunoonyereza kw'omutendera III ku remdesivir kwali kuwedde.
Nga Apuli 2020, okunoonyereza okwaliwo ku ngeri eddagala eriyitibwa COVID-19 gye lyakolebwamu n'engeri gye lyakolebwamu ku nsonga z'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 kwatandika. Okugeza, eddagala eddala eriyitibwa remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga lirina ekikozesebwa ne interferon beta, nabyo byekenneenyezebwa.
Okutuusa mu March 2020, waliwo ebiwandiiko ebisooka ku ngeri remdesivir gy'ekola obulungi.
Obulungi bwalabikira mu balwadde abaafuna remdesivir ng'ekyewuunyo.
Ekitundu ekyokusatu eky'okugezesebwa mu Amerika, China ne Italy, okusooka okukozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bwa malaria, kyatandika okukolebwa mu China mu Febwali 2020 era waliwo ebivudde mu kusooka.
Wadde kiri kityo, waliwo obwetaavu bw'okunoonyereza.
Ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu Korea ne China bakubiriza okukozesa kloroquine.
Ekitongole kya Wuhan Virology Institute kibuulirira eddagala erimu erya gram emu buli lunaku, kyokka nga kigamba nti okuddaabiriza eddaala lino kya kabi nnyo era kiyinza okuviirako omuntu okufa.
Nga 28 Maaki 2020, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa eddagala lya hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine mu mbeera ez'amangu nga abasawo bwe baagala nga bajjanjaba abalwadde ba COVID-19.
Ebyafaayo biraga nti eddagala eriyitibwa ribavirin eringi lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro.
Nitasoxanid yakubirizibwa okunoonyereza mu bujjuvu mu vivo, ng'alaga okulemesa SARS-CoV-2 mu bungi obutonotono. Okunoonyereza kwalaga nti okusobola okuyingira SARS-CoV-2 ng'eyita mu ACE2 receptor, kyetaagisa okutabagana kwa protein ya spine ne transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2).
Okunoonyereza ku kukozesa chlorokine ne hydroxychloroquine nga n'azithromycin oba nedda, birina obuzibu obw'amaanyi obulemesa abasawo okukozesa obujjanjabi buno nga tebannanoonyereza. Ozeltamavir teziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro, era ekifo kyayo mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19 tekimanyiddwa.
Okuyingiza obusimu obw'omubiri mu mubiri mu ngeri ey'obukambwe mu COVID-19 kiyinza okuvaamu obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine esobola okuba n'obuyinza ku ky'okusaasaanya obusaasaanya bw'omubiri. Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka China National Health Commission, tosilizumab yayingizibwa mu kubuulirira okukwata ku bulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe.
Eddagala lino lyafuluma mu kigezo kya 2 ekitali kya randomized ekikolebwa mu ggwanga lya Italy oluvannyuma lw'okufuna ebibala ebirungi mu bakozesa abalwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Bwe kikozesebwa awamu n'okunoonyereza ku musaayi gw'omuntu okulaba obanga alina eddagala eriyitibwa ferritin, kisobola okuyamba omuntu okwewala ebintu ebiyinza okumuviirako okufa.
Mu 2017, FDA yakkiriza interleukin-6 receptor antagonist okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku nsonga ez'edda okujjanjaba steroidal refractory cytokine release syndrome eyava ku nsonga endala, CAR T-cell therapy.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bukakafu bwonna bulaga nti tocilizumab ya mugaso mu kujjanjaba obulwadde bwa cytokine.
Okuwa abantu abaagala eddagala ery'okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa COVID-19 ebirwadde ebiggiddwa mu mubiri n'ebirwadde ebiruma omubiri, kati kitwalibwa ng'enkola ey'okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Enkola eno yagezeseddwa mu kujjanjaba abalwadde ba SARS, naye ebyavaamu tebyali birungi.
Okuggyawo akawuka  kye kintu ekisuubirwa ekireeta eddagala eririmu ebirungo okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enkola endala, gamba ng'obutabaako buwuka bwa bulwadde bwa butoffaali obuva ku mubiri oba obuva ku butoffaali, zisobola okukozesebwa.
Engeri endala ez'okujjanjaba n'omubiri ogumu, gamba ng'okukozesa omubiri ogumu ogukozesebwa mu kusannyalala, zikyali mu kutandikibwawo.
Okukozesa eddagala erikola ku musaayi oguva mu mulwadde eyawonawo era nga lirina ebirwanyisa akawuka kano, kiyinza okugaziwa.
